  "wechat_html": "<section style=\"margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f6efe4 0%,#fbf8f2 58%,#ffffff 100%);padding:1px;color:#1f2937;\"><section style=\"width:100%;margin:0;\"><section style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.16);box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:relative;background:#d6d3d1;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-00.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;display:block;\"></div><section style=\"padding:16px 12px 10px;\"><div style=\"display:inline-block;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:#111827;color:#f9fafb;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">History Today</div><h1 style=\"font-size:29px;line-height:1.22;margin:12px 0 10px;color:#111827;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;\">今日历史：改变世界的瞬间</h1><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#475569;margin:0;\">回顾3月12日发生的关键历史事件与纪念日。</p></section><section style=\"padding:0 10px 12px;\"><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">3月12日是一个充满历史印记的日子。世界范围内的多个纪念日提醒我们关注互联网自由，而远在印度洋的模里西斯也在今日庆祝其独立日。这些日子不仅是时间的刻度，更是人类文明进程的见证。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-01.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">追溯到公元前515年，耶路撒冷圣殿在波斯帝国大流士一世的支持下完成重建。这一建筑不仅是历史的丰碑，也标志着当时区域文化与宗教格局的重要转折点。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-02.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">时间来到1088年，拉热里的奥图正式当选为天主教会第159任教宗，即乌尔巴诺二世。他后来因发起十字军东征而闻名于世，深刻影响了中世纪的欧洲与地中海历史走向。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-03.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">在欧洲版图上，1158年的这一天，慕尼黑首次出现在神圣罗马帝国皇帝腓特烈一世的奥格斯堡仲裁文件中。这座城市从此开启了它作为欧洲重要文化与经济中心的漫长历史篇章。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-04.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">历史长河中，1316年塞尔维亚国王斯特凡·德拉古廷在这一天逝世。此外，1270年出生的瓦卢瓦伯爵等人物也为历史增添了多元色彩。这些往事共同构成了我们今日所处的复杂而宏大的世界。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-05.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div></section></section></section></section>"
